Arconic (NASDAQ: ARNC) and Alcoa Corp. (NYSE:AA) are both mid-cap basic materials companies, but which is the better stock? We will contrast the two companies based on the strength of their dividends, institutional ownership, valuation, analyst recommendations, risk, earnings and profitabiliy. 
